was your season
of internet stars?

00:18:47.050 --> 00:18:48.980
PHIL KEOGHAN: Another
fact that I didn't know.

00:18:48.980 --> 00:18:50.282
I love another fun fact.

00:18:50.282 --> 00:18:50.990
Another fun fact.

00:18:50.990 --> 00:18:51.320
CINDY HALVORSEN:
Here's another one.

