we used like a giant
catapult system going back

00:19:16.680 --> 00:19:18.777
to the old medieval times.

00:19:18.777 --> 00:19:21.110
That was sort of designed on
one of those old catapults.

00:19:21.110 --> 00:19:26.005
Anyway, we had a team, and
they were from a home shopping

00:19:26.005 --> 00:19:26.630
network, right?

