Am I right?

00:19:26.780 --> 00:19:27.240
CINDY HALVORSEN: Yes.

00:19:27.240 --> 00:19:28.560
Yeah, Brook and Claire.

00:19:28.560 --> 00:19:29.850
PHIL KEOGHAN: Yeah, Brook
